    <note>Wu(3) Jian(6) [1979] See documentation for brother, Bing(2) [22382]. Anhui TZ, 154.10b has jinshi in Yuanfeng, but other sources have him earning a decree exam degree in 1097 and he was active in 1134, which would make 1097 more logical. He may have been quite young when he earned the jinshi and passed the decree exam later. He was the son-in-law of Xiang(2) Minzhong's [705] great grandson and Empress Xiang(2)'s [4217] unnamed nephew, Xiang(2) A [4163]. XNYL, 81.7b. CBD, 2, 1086-7.</note>
